cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep generative priors and inverse problems in complex data such as images and text, which are typically studied in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of MAP estimation and the analysis of its performance in multi-layer networks further supports these categories.
